                <note rend="inline" type="source">611.5231/539: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Spain</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hammond</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1927-10-20T18:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 20, 1927—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>76. Your 103, October 18, 10 a.m. and 104, October 20, noon. Department of
                    Agriculture has cabled instructions to Kisliuk care your Embassy authorizing
                    Canary Islands investigation. Kisliuk has also been instructed to defer
                    publication of report of his investigation until after his return to the United
                    States.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
